Melakukan proses migrasi 
dari data warehouse menuju
 datamart

properties.SQL select query:
SELECT 
YEAR(CURDATE()) - stg_demography.dateofbirth as age,
stg_absence.firstname,
stg_activity.lastname,
stg_jobarchitecture.jobtitle,
stg_jobarchitecture.attrition,
stg_activity.businesstravel,
stg_compensation.dailyrate,
stg_jobarchitecture.jobdirect,
stg_demography.distancefromhome,
stg_demography.education,
stg_demography.educationfield,
stg_absence.employeenumber,
stg_survey.environmentsatisfaction,
stg_demography.gender,
stg_compensation.hourlyrate,
stg_activity.jobinvolvement,
stg_jobarchitecture.joblevel,
stg_survey.jobsatisfaction,
stg_demography.maritalstatus,
stg_compensation.monthlyincome,
stg_compensation.monthlyrate,
stg_jobarchitecture.numcompaniesworked,
CASE 
	WHEN YEAR(CURDATE()) - stg_demography.dateofbirth >= 18 THEN 'True'
    ELSE 'False'
END AS over18,
CASE 
	WHEN HOUR(SUBTIME(stg_absence.clockout, stg_absence.clockin)) >= 8 THEN true
    ELSE false
END AS overtime,
stg_compensation.percentsalaryhike,
stg_performance.performancerating,
stg_survey.relationshipsatisfaction,
stg_compensation.stockoptionlevel,
stg_jobarchitecture.totalworkingyears,
stg_performance.trainingtimeslastyear,
stg_survey.worklifebalance,
stg_jobarchitecture.yearsatcompany,
stg_jobarchitecture.yearsincurrentrole,
stg_jobarchitecture.yearssincelastpromotion,
stg_jobarchitecture.yearswithcurrmanager,
YEAR(CURDATE()) - stg_jobarchitecture.yearsatcompany as yearofentry
FROM stg_absence
INNER JOIN stg_activity ON stg_absence.employeenumber = stg_activity.employeenumber
INNER JOIN stg_compensation ON stg_activity.employeenumber = stg_compensation.employeenumber
INNER JOIN stg_demography ON stg_compensation.employeenumber = stg_demography.employeenumber
INNER JOIN stg_jobarchitecture ON stg_demography.employeenumber = stg_jobarchitecture.employeenumber
INNER JOIN stg_performance ON stg_jobarchitecture.employeenumber = stg_performance.employeenumber
INNER JOIN stg_survey ON stg_performance.employeenumber = stg_survey.employeenumber;

labels.label:
Merupakan proses aggregating 
dari 7 tabel staging menuju 
data warehouse di mysql

FLOW UTAMA
1. Staging proses : mengambil 7 data source/domain menuju data staging di mysql
2. updating with OCR : melakukan pelengkapan data kedalam beberapa kolow tabel 
yang masih NULL
3. aggregating proses : melakukan final join 7 tabel staging ke data warehouse
4. migrasi data warehouse menuju data mart untuk dikonsumsi oleh tools visualisasi
